'''诺曼·雷·伯德韦尔'''（{{lang-en|'''Norman Ray Bridwell'''}}，{{bd|1928年|2月15日|2014年|12月12日|catIdx=Bridwell}}），是一名美国作家、卡通家，他的作品以儿童读物《[[超级红卜卜|超级红卜卜]]》闻名。

==早期生涯==
1928年<ref name="AmBio">{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/Norman-Bridwell/e/B000APB74S/ |title=Norman Bridwell |publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2015-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731093620/http://www.amazon.com/Norman-Bridwell/e/B000APB74S |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，诺曼·雷·伯德韦尔出生于[[印第安那州|印第安那州]][[科克摩市|科克摩市]]<ref name="HCMP">{{cite web |url=http://www.howardcountymemory.net/default.aspx?id=9356 |title=Norman Bridwell - ''Never Give Up on Your Dreams'' |year=2009 |work=Howard County Memory Project |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2017-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923120948/http://www.howardcountymemory.net/default.aspx?id=9356 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1945年，他毕业于{{le|科克摩高中|Kokomo High School}}<ref name="HCMP" />，之后进入印第安纳波利斯的{{le|约翰·赫伦艺术学院|John Herron School of Art}}<ref name="KR">{{cite web |url=http://www.kidsreads.com/authors/au-bridwell-norman.asp |work=KidsReads |title=Biography: Norman Bridwell |year=2012 |publisher=The Book Report Network |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106030224/http://www.kidsreads.com/authors/au-bridwell-norman.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，后转入纽约市的[[库伯联盟学院|库伯联盟学院]]<ref name="KR" />。

==事业==
诺曼·伯德韦尔开始绘画，并以儿童读物插画师开始寻求工作，但是他被近十五所出版商拒绝<ref name="KR" />。当他在{{le|哈珀与罗出版公司|Harper (publisher)}}寻找机会时，一名编辑随口建议他将绘画作品写入故事。他听从了这个建议，并将小女儿和房子一样大的血猎犬克利福德的故事，写成《超级红卜卜》<ref name="KR" />。该书随后带动了四十多部克利福德系列畅销书<ref name="KR" />、两部电视剧<ref name="PBS">{{cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/parents/clifford/about_program/program_summary.html |title=Program Summary: ''Clifford The Big Red Dog'' and ''Clifford's Puppy Days'' |work=Parents & Teachers |publisher=[[PBS|PBS]] |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924150807/http://www.pbs.org/parents/clifford/about_program/program_summary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、各类产品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://clifford.shop.pbskids.org/ |title=Clifford The Big Red Dog |work=Shop PBS Kids |publisher=[[PBS|PBS]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102112625/http://clifford.shop.pbskids.org/ |archivedate=2012-01-02 |access-date=2015-08-04 }}</ref>、以及音乐片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scholastic.com/clifford/parentsteachers/liveshow.htm |title=Clifford The Big Red Dog Live Show |publisher=[[Scholastic_Corporation|Scholastic]] |date=January 2012 |access-date=2015-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111072419/http://www.scholastic.com/clifford/parentsteachers/liveshow.htm |archive-date=2012-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

伯德韦尔的其他畅销书有《隔壁的女巫》、《微小的家》，他的著作也有近1.26亿本，并翻译至13种语言<ref name="AmBio" />。

==个人生活==
1962年，伯德韦尔娶诺玛·霍华德为妻<ref name=TWPBridwellDies>{{cite news|last1=Langer|first1=Emily|title=Norman Bridwell, writer and illustrator who created Clifford the Big Red Dog, dies at 86|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/norman-bridwell-writer-and-illustrator-who-created-clifford-the-big-red-dog-dies-at-86/2014/12/17/03a91550-8604-11e4-b9b7-b8632ae73d25_story.html|accessdate=December 20, 2014|work=The Washington Post|date=December 17, 2014|archive-date=2015-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805003524/http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/norman-bridwell-writer-and-illustrator-who-created-clifford-the-big-red-dog-dies-at-86/2014/12/17/03a91550-8604-11e4-b9b7-b8632ae73d25_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并有一女艾米丽·伊丽莎白和一子蒂莫西<ref name="EW">{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,277463,00.html |title=Living A Dog's Life: Norman Bridwell |first=Bruce |last=Fretts |date=September 8, 2000 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2014-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217062933/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,277463,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/16/showbiz/celebrity-news-gossip/feat-obit-norman-bridwell-clifford-big-red-dog/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|title=Norman Bridwell, creator of 'Clifford the Big Red Dog,' dead at 86|first=Todd|last=Leopold|date=December 16, 2014|accessdate=December 18, 2014|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924175421/http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/16/showbiz/celebrity-news-gossip/feat-obit-norman-bridwell-clifford-big-red-dog/index.html?hpt=hp_t2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他们家族在1969年迁居至[[马沙文雅岛|马沙文雅岛]]<ref name="EW" />。2014年12月12日，伯德韦尔因心脏衰竭去世，享年86岁<ref name=MVTimesDead>{{cite news|url=http://www.mvtimes.com/2014/12/16/norman-ray-bridwell-beloved-author-clifford-big-red-dog-dead-86/|title=Norman Ray Bridwell, beloved author of Clifford the Big Red Dog, dead at 86|newspaper=Martha's Vineyard Times|date=December 16, 2014|accessdate=December 16, 2014|archive-date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104185250/http://www.mvtimes.com/2014/12/16/norman-ray-bridwell-beloved-author-clifford-big-red-dog-dead-86/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

